type="place">Taormina</rs><note type="commentary" xml:id="KL1927-02-26_01_AS_Hofmannsthal-1h"><ref target="1904-05-19" subtype="cf" type="schnitzlerDiary"/></note> u <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="KL1927-02-26_01_AS_Hofmannsthal-2"/><rs ref="#pmb1281" type="place">Syrakus</rs><note type="commentary" xml:id="KL1927-02-26_01_AS_Hofmannsthal-2h"><ref target="1904-05-17" type="schnitzlerDiary" subtype="cf"/></note>.</p><closer>Herzlichst Ihr <signed>Arthur</signed></closer></div></body></text></TEI>